casebody.data:
No. 301,

Misc.

Bailey v. DeQuevedo. Peter O. Clauss for petitioner. Solicitor General Marshall, Acting Assistant Attorney General Eardley, John C. Eldridge and Robert V. Zener for respondent.

C. A. 3d Cir. Certiorari denied.

. Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted. Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
